<%- include('../partials/header') %>

<section class="page-header">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    <p>Find answers to common questions about our platform</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="faq">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="faq-container">
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question">
          <h3>How do I access course materials?</h3>
          <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>Once you enroll in a course, you'll gain access to all course materials through your student dashboard. Materials typically include video lectures, reading materials, and practice exercises.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question">
          <h3>Are there any prerequisites for courses?</h3>
          <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>Prerequisites vary by course. Each course page lists any required prior knowledge or experience. Some courses are designed for beginners, while others may require some foundational knowledge.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question">
          <h3>How do I join live sessions?</h3>
          <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>Live sessions can be accessed through the link provided in your course dashboard. You'll receive email reminders before each session with the link and any preparation materials.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question">
          <h3>Are live sessions recorded?</h3>
          <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>Yes, all live sessions are recorded and made available within 24 hours after the session ends. You can access recordings through your course dashboard.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question">
          <h3>How do I contact my instructor?</h3>
          <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>You can contact instructors through the messaging system in your course dashboard or by using the email address listed on their profile page.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question">
          <h3>What if I miss a live session?</h3>
          <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>Don't worry if you miss a live session. All sessions are recorded and made available in your course dashboard. You can also post questions in the course forum for the instructor to answer.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<%- include('../partials/footer') %>